---
---

<section class="success-stories reveal" id="work">
    <div class="success-stories__content">
        <div class="success-stories__cards">
            <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-1" style="flex: 0 0 400px;">
                <div class="success-stories__card-header">
                    <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Architecture</span>
                    <span class="success-stories__card-status">COMPLETED</span>
                </div>
                <span class="success-stories__card-metric">40% cost reduction</span>
                <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">SAAS PLATFORM REBUILD</h3>
                <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Architecture overhaul of a multi-tenant SaaS platform serving 200+ enterprise clients. Migrated from monolithic PHP to distributed Node.js, tripling throughput.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-2" style="flex: 0 0 340px;">
                <div class="success-stories__card-header">
                    <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Leadership</span>
                    <span class="success-stories__card-status">COMPLETED</span>
                </div>
                <span class="success-stories__card-metric">12-person team</span>
                <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">SCALE-UP TEAM BUILDING</h3>
                <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Built an engineering team from scratch. Established hiring pipelines, onboarding, and code review culture that cut deploy time from weeks to hours.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-3" style="flex: 0 0 380px;">
                <div class="success-stories__card-header">
                    <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Infrastructure</span>
                    <span class="success-stories__card-status">COMPLETED</span>
                </div>
                <span class="success-stories__card-metric">99.99% uptime</span>
                <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">CLOUD MIGRATION</h3>
                <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Migrated a legacy monolith to cloud-native microservices on AWS — zero downtime, 5M records preserved, 60% infrastructure cost reduction.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-4" style="flex: 0 0 320px;">
                <div class="success-stories__card-header">
                    <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Product Dev</span>
                    <span class="success-stories__card-status">COMPLETED</span>
                </div>
                <span class="success-stories__card-metric">3x conversions</span>
                <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">E-COMMERCE RELAUNCH</h3>
                <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Rebuilt a failing e-commerce platform end-to-end, delivering 3x conversion rate improvement and 60% faster page loads.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="success-stories__cta-row">
            <a class="success-stories__cta" href="#contact">BOOK A CALL</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
    .success-stories {
        padding: 80px 0 48px 144px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 32px;

        &__content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 48px;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        &__cards {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            gap: 16px;
            align-items: flex-start;
            overflow-x: auto;
            padding-bottom: 16px;
            padding-right: 48px;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;

            &::-webkit-scrollbar { height: 4px; }
            &::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: rgba(252, 227, 0, 0.04); }
            &::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(252, 227, 0, 0.15); }
        }

        &__card {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(252, 227, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 24px 20px;
            clip-path: polygon(0 0, calc(100% - 14px) 0, 100% 14px, 100% 100%, 14px 100%, 0 calc(100% - 14px));
            transition: border-color 0.2s ease;

            &:hover {
                border-color: rgba(252, 227, 0, 0.3);
            }
        }

        &__card-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        &__card-tag {
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.6875rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 3px 10px;
            background: rgba(252, 227, 0, 0.1);
            color: var(--clr-yellow);
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        &__card-status {
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.625rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--clr-cyan);
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        }

        &__card-metric {
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
            color: var(--clr-yellow);
        }

        &__card-title {
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fff;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        &__card-desc {
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        &__cta-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding-right: 144px;
        }

        &__cta {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            color: var(--clr-bg-primary);
            background: var(--clr-yellow);
            padding: 12px 40px;
            clip-path: polygon(0 0, calc(100% - 10px) 0, 100% 10px, 100% 100%, 10px 100%, 0 calc(100% - 10px));
            transition: background-color 0.15s ease;

            &:hover { background: var(--clr-cyan); }
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1440px) {
        .success-stories { padding: 64px 0 40px 80px; &__cta-row { padding-right: 80px; } }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .success-stories {
            padding: 64px 2rem;
            &__cards { flex-direction: column; overflow-x: visible; padding-right: 0; }
            &__card { flex: none !important; width: 100%; }
            &__cta-row { padding-right: 0; }
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 375px) {
        .success-stories { padding: 64px 1.25rem; &__cta-row { padding-right: 0; } }
    }
</style>
